				<div id="post-39" class="post-39 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-gardening tag-heirloom-vegatables tag-monsanto tag-organic-gardening tag-seed-saving tag-survival-planning">
					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-23- The Role of Heirloom Vegetables in Survival Planning</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/the-role-of-heirloom-vegetables-in-survival-planning" title="4:13 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">July 25, 2008</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/the-role-of-heirloom-vegetables-in-survival-planning#comments" title="Comment on Episode-23- The Role of Heirloom Vegetables in Survival Planning">8 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<div id="tweetbutton39" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fthe-role-of-heirloom-vegetables-in-survival-planning&amp;text=Episode-23-%20The%20Role%20of%20Heirloom%20Vegetables%20in%20Survival%20Planning&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fthe-role-of-heirloom-vegetables-in-survival-planning" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
